svg.text: Timed Switch Activator (22) Activates switch for a set time (e.g. temporarily activates laser door).
Timed Switch Deactivator (23) Deactivates switch for a set time (e.g. temporarily deactivates laser door).
Switch Activator (24) Activates switch (e.g. activates laser door).
Switch Deactivator (25) Deactivates switch (e.g. deactivates laser door).
Freeze (9) Freezes (stuns) for a couple of seconds (for 3 seconds by default).
Heart (198) Freezes (stuns) for 3 seconds.
Deep (12) Freezes (stuns) permanently, cancelled only by undeep.
Undeep (13) Cancels Deep freeze effect.
Hit Others On (19) Enables hitting others with weapons.
Hit Others Off (20) Disables hitting others with weapons.
Time Penalty (79) Adds a set amount of seconds to your timer.
Time Bonus (95) Subtracts a set amount of seconds off your timer.
Evil Teleporter Gun Block (98) Can be teleported with teleporter guns, tees lose their speed on teleporting.
Teleporter Gun Block (99) Can be teleported to with teleporter guns, tees keep their speed on teleporting.
Live Freeze (144) Disables movement keys permanently, cancelled only by live unfreeze.
Live Unfreeze (145) Cancels live freeze effect.
Shield (197) Takes all collectable weapons away: shotgun, grenade, laser and ninja.
Shotgun Shield (226) Takes shotgun away.
Grenade Shield (227) Takes grenade away.
Ninja Shield (228) Takes ninja away.
Laser Shield (229) Takes laser away.
Shotgun (199) Weapon, shoots beam that bounces off walls and pulls the first tee it hits.
Grenade Launcher (200) Weapon, shoots exploding projectile in an arc.
Ninja (201) Weapon, lasts 15 seconds at max, allows you to dash, you can't use other weapons while you have ninja.
Laser (202) Weapon, shoots beam that bounces off walls and unfreezes the first tee it hits.
Counterclockwise, Fast Rotating Freezing Laser (203) Center of a continuous laser beam that freezes tees and rotates counterclockwise.
Counterclockwise, Normal Rotating Freezing Laser (204) Center of a continuous laser beam that freezes tees and rotates counterclockwise.
Counterclockwise, Slow Rotating Freezing Laser (205) Center of a continuous laser beam that freezes tees and rotates counterclockwise.
Clockwise, Slow Rotating Freezing Laser (207) Center of a continuous laser beam that freezes tees and rotates clockwise.
Clockwise, Normal Rotating Freezing Laser (208) Center of a continuous laser beam that freezes tees and rotates clockwise.
Clockwise, Fast Rotating Freezing Laser (209) Center of a continuous laser beam that freezes tees and rotates clockwise.
Laser Length Setter (210) Sets the length of a laser door or rotating laser to 3 tiles.
Laser Length Setter (211) Sets the length of a laser door or rotating laser to 6 tiles.
Laser Length Setter (212) Sets the length of a laser door or rotating laser to 9 tiles.
Slow Laser Lengthener (213) Causes laser length to lengthen and shorten, doesn't work with laser doors.
Normal Laser Lengthener (214) Causes laser length to lengthen and shorten, doesn't work with laser doors.
Fast Laser Lengthener (215) Causes laser length to lengthen and shorten, doesn't work with laser doors.
Slow Laser Length Changer (216) Causes laser length to shorten and lengthen, doesn't work with laser doors.
Normal Laser Length Changer (217) Causes laser length to shorten and lengthen, doesn't work with laser doors.
Fast Laser Length Changer (218) Causes laser length to shorten and lengthen, doesn't work with laser doors.
Explosion Turret (220) Locks onto the nearest tee and shoots projectiles at it that explode. Doesn't work through walls and turret blocker tiles.
Freeze Turret (221) Locks onto the nearest tee and shoots projectiles at it that freeze for 3 seconds. Doesn't work through walls and turret blocker tiles.
Freeze Explosion Turret (222) Locks onto the nearest tee and shoots projectiles at it that explode and freeze for 3 seconds. Doesn't work through walls and turret blocker tiles.
Unfreeze Turret (223) Locks onto the nearest tee and shoots projectiles at it that unfreezes. Doesn't work through walls and turret blocker tiles.
Exploding Bullet (224) Moving projectile that freezes it hits and explodes when bouncing off walls.
Bullet (225) Moving projectile that freezes it hits and bounces off walls.
Slow Dragger (233) Locks onto closest tee and drags it until it is out of sight again, blocked by walls and dragger blocker tiles.
Normal Dragger (234) Locks onto closest tee and drags it until it is out of sight again, blocked by walls and dragger blocker tiles.
Fast Dragger (235) Locks onto closest tee and drags it until it is out of sight again, blocked by walls and dragger blocker tiles.
Slow Hookthrough Dragger (236) Locks onto closest tee and drags it until it is out of sight again, blocked only by dragger blocker tiles.
Normal Hookthrough Dragger (237) Locks onto closest tee and drags it until it is out of sight again, blocked only by dragger blocker tiles.
Fast Hookthrough Dragger (238) Locks onto closest tee and drags it until it is out of sight again, blocked only by dragger blocker tiles.
Empty (0) Empty tile, used as an eraser in the map editor.
Jump Count Setter (7) Sets the amount of jumps available to you (2 by default).
Credits (140) Designer of the entities.
Static Freezing Laser (206) Continuous laser beam that freezes tees.
Laser Door (240) Doesn't let tees through, controlled by switches and works like a row of stopper tiles.
